ABOUT US
The Anchor Inn has been owned by Bob and Darla Tingler since April 1st, 1994. Together, they have been in the building since 1985, when Bob began as just a bartender. The Anchor is a family owned establishment, with both sons, Joey and Robby, now tending bar. Needless to say The Anchor Inn crew is very much family, and that feeling carries over to local clientele as well. As always, everyone is welcome, and no one is “too good” for The Anchor.  At the end of the day, The Anchor Inn is an old school, smoking, dive bar that offers a home type feeling, to locals and tourists alike. The Anchor Inn is open 7 am to 3 am (Closed Thanksgiving and Christmas), allowing you to come stop by for a drink almost anytime! We look forward to seeing you at The Anchor Inn, where we’ll be
“Living the Dream”!
